{"ts":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z","author":"codex-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-55ra"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Token-budget context packer: diversity-aware selection, projection degradation, and bounded output for pm context/next"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Turn ranked candidates into the most useful bounded-token context packet, shrinking projections before dropping relevant work."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["context","relevance","scale","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":360},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm context and pm next accept or derive an explicit token budget; packer preserves high-scoring required items, avoids near-duplicate context clusters, degrades projection depth before item omission, and reports budget accounting in json/debug output; behavior is measured by pm-cu1i token corpus and pm-atfm quality judgments; large-workspace output remains bounded by contract."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-4k6b"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-atfm","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z","author":"codex-agent"},{"id":"pm-cu1i","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z","author":"codex-agent"},{"id":"pm-dfg0","kind":"blocked_by","created_at":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z","author":"codex-agent"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-06T23:50:39.960Z","author":"codex-agent","text":"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for token budget packer/projection degradation/context ranking; existing items cover token measurement and pagination, but no packer implementation item existed."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"f53c17350bd6d8743b17b971ee78fbac9515fee1e150f299da8daed10175a462","message":""}
