{"ts":"2026-07-12T19:07:34.082Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-12T19:07:34.082Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-12T19:07:34.082Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Scope addition 2026-07-12 (pm-4k6b algorithms (18)+(19), definitions on that ledger): the packer surface owns (a) the explicit latency-budget parameter with threshold-algorithm early termination and a disclosed completeness certificate + degradation ladder in the envelope (algorithm 18), and (b) the task-set profile table keyed by triggering intent, with active-profile disclosure and safety-signal mask-immunity (algorithm 19). Learned-profile graduation is pm-uwfs (wave 4), not here."}]}],"before_hash":"7c1cd428f65a7d9f70527ffdfa09e541b93b941e4986ea0f0832dc4a2593f983","after_hash":"2e7867bff4d524a8ce0ddefc6260f9157caef6ca3bd0a6b9b75820adb8c15770"}
{"ts":"2026-07-13T17:50:53.366Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T17:50:53.366Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Packer hooks from pm-4k6b directed pass 2026-07-13 (additions to this item's existing (18) deadline contract + (19) profile table ownership): (a) algorithm (21) risk-adjusted marginal value — packing consumes each estimate's credible width, value = mean - lambda*sigma with lambda selectable per (19) profile, so uncertain high-scorers can enter at reduced projection instead of full verbatim; --explain-ranking discloses the evidence basis (n, raw, shrunk, prior). (b) algorithm (22) lineage dedupe — lineage-mates count as near-duplicates in the (4) redundancy penalty; only the best chain representative spends budget, carrying a lineage breadcrumb for drill-down. Definitions in the pm-4k6b ledger, algorithms (21)-(22)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T17:50:53.366Z"}],"before_hash":"2e7867bff4d524a8ce0ddefc6260f9157caef6ca3bd0a6b9b75820adb8c15770","after_hash":"7280c761ed7be0cdd70ae9bae2db41b5296ff18cab3a8bb380cb8534f0b671f8"}
